  "id": "PLACE_nocturn_ashwood",
  "label": "Nocturn Ashwood",
  "description": "Nocturn Ashwood is a dense temperate forest on Cyrenth Vale, rooted in ash-laden soils laid down by centuries of atmospheric fallout. Its trunks rise tall and close-set, their bark stained dark by soot and mineral deposition, while the canopy filters the planet’s cold, veiled luminance into a perpetual dusk. Bruise-hued aurorae from the rift-shadowed sky flicker across wet leaves and lichen, casting intermittent color through the understory. The ground is threaded with shallow gullies and slag-strewn clearings that preserve the marks of long siege logistics and neglected perimeter works.",
